Text: FW RaceCarClub Party Friday October wwwracecarclubn etHope you can make it Original Message From mailtoOn Behalf Of Jessica Rossman Sent Friday September PM To info Subject RaceCarClub Party Friday October wwwracecarclubnet Rev up your engines and prepare for an evening built for speed The RaceCarClub and QUIERO PISCO invite you to the third annual RaceCarClub party cohosted for the first time with the TexacoHavoline Grand Prix Friday October from pm until am at the historic Rice Lofts Celebrate Houstons TexacoHavoline Grand Prix with the velocity for which the RaceCarClub is known as QUIERO PISCO and a revved up roster of Houstons own social racing hosts steer the RaceCarClub fun at the Rice that evening The Empire Room will feature Houstons own and Houston Press Best New Artist nominee Arthur Yoria wwwarthuryoriacom along with the El Orbits on the balcony and a plethora of some of downtowns hottest DJs in the Crystal Ballroom and five open bars with free flowing bottomless cocktails featuring Houston hottest new Latin import QUIERO PISCO Fashionable attire is a requisite along with your allinclusive entrance fee presale online or Market Price as available at the door To help those effected by the bearish economy this year we are offering a reduced price of for the first tickets sold so act fast and save a few bucks A portion of the evenings proceeds will be donated to the Muscular Dystrophy Association To make your evening and pocket stretch a little further this year your RaceCarClub pass waives the cover charge at the following downtown bars the evening of the event Club Grasshopper Prague Shot Bar Mercury Room Spy To buy your tickets or for more information please visit our web site at wwwracecarclubnet If you have any questions andor comments please feel free to contact Martin Productions Inc at or Please forward this email along to others that might enjoy the evening RaceCarClub is brought to you by QUIERO PISCO Houstons newest spirit imported from Latin America for your partying pleasure To unsubscribe send an email to with UNSUBSCRIBE QPINFO in the BODY of the message The information contained in this communication is confidential and proprietary information intended only for the individual or entity to whom it is addressed Any unauthorized use distribution copying or disclosure of this communication is strictly prohibited If you have received this communication in error please contact the sender immediately If you believe this communication is inappropriate or offensive please contact Ocean Energys Human Resources Department
